  m_Name: NeighborJournal_08
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 25
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #8 \u2014 Logan Paul, c\u1EF1u chi\u1EBFn
    binh"
  category: 3
  content: "B\xE0 x\xE3 t\xF4i \u0111\xE3 bi\u1EBFn t\u1EEB \u0111\xEAm qua. T\xF4i
    tr\xF3i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c b\xE0 v\xE0o gh\u1EBF nh\u01B0ng ti\u1EBFng b\xE0
    k\xEAu... t\xF4i kh\xF4ng ch\u1ECBu n\u1ED5i. 78 tu\u1ED5i, s\u1ED1ng v\u1EDBi
    nhau 55 n\u0103m. T\xF4i vi\u1EBFt d\xF2ng n\xE0y r\u1ED3i s\u1EBD ra ngo\xE0i.
    \u0110\u1EA1n c\xF2n 3 vi\xEAn. Xin \u0111\u1EEBng tr\xE1ch t\xF4i. Cu\u1ED1n
    nh\u1EADt k\xFD n\xE0y \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i cho ai c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng trong khu
    ph\u1ED1. H\xE3y c\u1EA9n th\u1EADn, ch\xFAng kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    n\u1EEFa."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
